VegClub is arriving! 🛬

In collaboration with an undisclosed investor, vegan entrepreneur Will Callaghan is gearing up to launch VegClub Magazine. The magazine vows to encompass all aspects of food, shopping, and travel across Europe and the UK, focusing on the plant-based and sustainable market. 💚

Initially launching as a digital version, the ultimate goal is to transition into print, offering physical copies for those who prefer offline reading. The launch is set for May of this year. 🙌🏻
